name: Uesugi Kenshin (Rance series)
description:
For my second LoRA, another fan (and personal) favorite from the Rance games.
I'm pretty happy with how it turned out, my training data was heavily skewed towards her armored appearance, so those look pretty good as expected, but her clothing is more flexible than I anticipated, so that was a pleasant surprise. The only weaker point I saw is with explicit NSFW, I found that the nsfw tag messes with the quality a bit, so try to omit it if possible, otherwise it works fine, but it's not the main focus of this Lora (maybe in a future version).

Weight around 0.75 worked best for me.

The activation tag is uesugi kenshin (rance), which should cover her general appearance.
For her armored look these are useful: armor, helmet, hair ribbon.

meta.prompt: 1girl, solo, masterpiece, best quality, highly detailed, illustration, uesugi kenshin (rance), outdoors, village, east asian architecture, standing, armor, helmet, looking at viewer, expressionless, <lora:Kenshin-10:0.75>
meta.negativePrompt: (worst quality, low quality:1.3), bloom, blur, watermark, (malformed hands:1.4), (poorly drawn hands:1.4), (mutated fingers:1.4)
